                    skills that I believe will be valuable in the future such as website development and programming.
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    With the experiences in design that I have accumulated and the systematic way of thinking that I
                    have, I am now capable of making design decisions that understand the customer and their technical
                    needs without compromise on details.
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    Now with that in mind, I summarized my strong elements into 3 points:
                </p>
                <div class="points">
                    <div class="point-cell">
                        <div class="point-icon"><img src="assets/Logo/Points/tech-point.svg" alt="Technology Logo">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Technology and Computer Enthusiast</h3>
                        <p>I am a passionate designer obsessed with the latest trends in computers and technology.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="point-cell">
                        <div class="point-icon"><img src="assets/Logo/Points/fast-point.svg" alt="Technology Logo">
                        </div>
