                        <p>I consider myself a quick learner that is not afraid to learn any new skills or concepts that
                            can improve my skillset.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="point-cell">
                        <div class="point-icon"><img src="assets/Logo/Points/adapt-point.svg" alt="Technology Logo">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Systematic Thinking and Workflow</h3>
                        <p>My programming skills further how I set my workflow and it shows in how I design.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="paragraph center">
                    If you’d like to know more about me, please contact me.<br>
                    I am looking forward to your response.
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    Thank you.
                </p>
            </div>
